i  		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  $ dig +short @1.1.1.1 TXT whoami.lantian.pub		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  "[2400:cb00:12:1024::6ca2:d626]:16668"		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
